graph TD
    subgraph Producer System
        Cron[Cron Schedule] -->|Triggers| IDP[Image Discovery Producer]
        IDP -->|1. List & Filter| NOAA[NOAA S3]
        IDP -->|2. Check Exists| MinIO[MinIO S3]
        IDP -->|3. Check In-Progress| DB[(SQLite Tracker)]
        IDP -->|4. Publish| Q[RabbitMQ: tiles_work_queue]
    end

    subgraph Worker System
        Q -->|Consume| Worker[Worker Service]
        Worker -->|Dispatch| Router{Stage?}
        
        Router -->|DOWNLOAD| DL[Download Handler]
        Router -->|PROCESS| PH[Process Handler]
        
        subgraph Stage 1: Download
            DL -->|Download| LocalFile[Local NetCDF]
            DL -->|Publish Next| Q
        end

        subgraph Stage 2: Process Pipeline
            PH -->|Delegate| GP[GoesProcessor]
            GP -->|Step 1| Georef[Georeferencing]
            Georef -->|Step 2| BT[Brightness Temp]
            BT -->|Step 3| GT[GeoTIFF Gen]
            GT -->|Step 4| Tiles[Tile Gen gdal2tiles]
            Tiles -->|Step 5| Upload[Upload to MinIO]
            Upload -->|Step 6| Retention[Enforce Retention]
            Retention -->|Cleanup| Done[Mark Complete]
        end
    end

    style Q fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style IDP fill:#bbf,stroke:#333
    style Worker fill:#bbf,stroke:#333
